trans-unit.source: Wrapper class that represents attributes on a type at design time.
This class cannot be inherited.
> [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] This class is used to represent attributes on design-time types (types that are yet to be compiled).
This occurs only when validation is triggered through the designer.
Gets a collection that contains values for each of the arguments associated with this instance.
This collection is read-only.
A collection that contains values for each of the arguments associated with this instance.
Gets the <xref:System.Type> of this instance.
The <xref:System.Type> of this instance.
Gets a value that indicates whether this instance can be created.

Returns a value which is <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> if either of the following conditions are true: - The <xref:System.Type> defining this attribute has an <xref:System.Type.Assembly*> which is a null reference (Visual Basic <xref uid="langword_csharp_Nothing" name="Nothing" href=""></xref>). - Any one of the objects in the array <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.AttributeInfo.ArgumentValues*> is of <xref:System.Type><xref:System.Exception> Otherwise the value returned is <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>.
Creates an attribute of type Creates an attribute of type <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.AttributeInfo"></xref>.
An attribute of type <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.AttributeInfo"></xref>.
<xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.AttributeInfo.Creatable*> is <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
Gets the argument for this instance, based on type and index.
The <xref:System.IServiceProvider> helping this operation.
The <xref uid="langword_csharp_integer" name="integer" href=""></xref> index of the requested argument in the collection of arguments.
The <xref:System.Type> of the argument.
An <xref:System.Object> cast to the requested type.
argumentIndex is out of range of the argument collection.
requestedType is a null reference ( in Visual Basic).
